frenziedFrame.1=§7You don't know how it came to you... madness, is it not?<BR>You remember yourself swearing to others that you heard some kind of voice in the back of your mind, almost silently... screaming? You can vaguely remember its ghastly call, screaming for you to burn the world in the purifying flames of chaos.<BR>You took it into your hands, and you distinctly remember feeling the chaotic energies burning through your body, singeing your very mind in its fire.<BR><BR>But... surely you didn't, that would be madness after all...
