magicbees.botania.lexicon.manasteelTools.0=§7Manasteel's unusual properties lends itself well to Naturalist's tools. The &1Manasteel Scoop&0 can be used to effectively harvest hives, and the &1Manasteel Grafter&0 is a durable subsitute for the generic bronze grafters. Of course, both tools have the ability to regenerate with mana. For best results, combine the tool with Living Wood.
